{"tid":169170,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[最新發展]樹大工管生乞食物贊助，甩底賴發燒大話連篇","createTime":"2017-03-24T04:56:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-28T02:33:28.000Z","uid":7775,"like":29,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0b7bb07a5020595e012c949b247bb8058ec78da3","tid":169170,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T04:56:34.000Z","msg":"鑒於樹大同學上門道歉<span style=\"color: red;\">都仲係講緊大話</span><br />\n<br />\n到而家畀人感覺仲係誠意欠奉、逃避責任<br />\n<br />\n所以再開一個Post 跟進最新情況"},{"pid":"d80f1b7bfa7e4cddc41c1e95505ea959cc1b769f","tid":169170,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T05:00:17.000Z","msg":"先簡略講返個大要<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2月23日</span><br />\n樹仁大學工商管理學系系會幹事 何欣婷(Gillian Ho) 聯同另外4名幹事去紅磡串噹噹為學會3月10舉辦既「就職典禮」求食物贊助，對方答應提供魚蛋、雞翼各一盆。雙方同意樹仁當日18:00領取食物<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d15YsAV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd15YsAV.jpg&h=d287f16b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3月10日</span><br />\n串噹噹履行合約預先準備相關食物，可惜直到18:44 樹大工管仍沓無音訊。店方根據支莊提供既聯絡方式打電話，都無人聽/打唔通。<br />\n最後朋友搭上搭，幾經辛苦先至搵到班大帝<br />\n<br />\n獲得既回覆係:<br />\n「我地活動取消咗」，<span style=\"color: red;\">「好多同學發緊燒」</span>更狡辯話已經一早whatsapp 店主取消，店主要求相關紀錄不得要領<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幻覺黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/24/125848_c7f45fe153b1c0a240f7d8ba0cc4ccc1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F24%2F125848_c7f45fe153b1c0a240f7d8ba0cc4ccc1.jpg&h=d09bc76a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3月21日</span><br />\n明報報導事件，同日網民大規模炮轟相關樹大學生<br />\n<br />\n植金憑主席因此事隔11日後突然知錯，並於深夜寫出一封初中水平既道歉信以圖了事<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170321/s00001/149009889400/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170321%2Fs00001%2F149009889400%2F&d=JjpB%2FqIgFksXGEBY%2BN5axACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=72e25687\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170321%2Fs00001%2F149009889400%2F&h=7ebc4a4c\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170321/s00001/149009889400/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/24/125955_a5a3653ec5084758b2ebc8af7df28007.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F24%2F125955_a5a3653ec5084758b2ebc8af7df28007.jpg&h=9d5a1eff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3月22日</span><br />\n道歉信未能收效，反令狙擊火力有增無減，終於數名幹事上門道歉並解釋事情<br />\n(佢地聲稱21日都有上去但唔見人，依個無從求證，講慣大話唔太可信)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3月23日</span><br />\n頭條日報 亦對事情作出報導<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/daily/hk/551726/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Fdaily%2Fhk%2F551726%2F&d=JjpB%2FqIgFksXGEBY%2BN5axACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=7e64c909\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Fdaily%2Fhk%2F551726%2F&h=6697c521\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/daily/hk/551726/</a>"},{"pid":"fe201ac24d464533c800b59342e8c5e4ddfb1435","tid":169170,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T05:01:13.000Z","msg":"子曰：「言忠信，行篤敬，雖蠻貊之邦行矣；言不忠信，行不篤敬，雖州里行乎哉？立，則見其參於前也；在輿，則見其倚於衡也。夫然後行。」"},{"pid":"899a242885debadc306c8a7441f23187f6124225","tid":169170,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T05:01:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">最新發展</span><br />\n店主個女聯繫小弟Facebook 專頁<br />\n傾過下，交換意見，大要如下:<br />\n<br />\n1. 證實3月21真係有人落黎道歉，但唔係全莊；<br />\n2. 店方拒絕對方任何金錢上賠償；<br />\n3. 當我問及佢原唔原諒相關人士，佢無直接答我，只係希望事情告一段落，但後尾關於狙擊行動講咗一句<br />\n「呢啲就交俾公眾，串噹噹可以講嘅講咗」"},{"pid":"b1fc4e2a711d7cd34edaaa808999625fa9719674","tid":169170,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T05:02:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">樹大係咪真係知錯？</span><br />\n小弟就覺得佢地毫無悔意，悔都係因為個後果而唔係行為本身<br />\n<br />\n1. 上報後突然知錯<br />\n之前一直潛水，側側膊扮無事<br />\n事隔11日上明報之後突然醒悟<br />\n<br />\n2. 公開信含糊不清<br />\n我唔再講文筆同表達問題，但係有心道歉係咪應該交代反事實係點？(e.g. 邊樣係真、邊樣係假，事情係點，講過咩大話)<br />\n只草草交代一句「以謊言掩飾本會之過失」好難收貨<br />\n<br />\n3. 上門道歉仍然堅持講大話<br />\n據店主個女get 到，樹仁班友當面解釋甩底原因係「係時間同交通安排問題」<br />\n<br />\n但係透過暗中起Sophia底既過程，發現就職典禮backdrop 根本無串噹噹既logo，有兩個可能性:<br />\n<br />\na. 一早忘記咗搵過串噹噹贊助<br />\n(可能性低，堆合約放埋一齊，無理由淨係串噹噹果份放開咗第二度)<br />\n<br />\nb. sponsor已經R得夠多，嫌人遠唔想攞，一早已經計劃好甩人底，諗住唔搵人側側膊當無事<br />\n(上過莊都知，文宣同backdrop 一早已經要整定)<br />\n<br />\na 同b都好，到而家班友都仲未肯講真話"},{"pid":"ab70341851614a53ac47f682ba1c16352d4b224a","tid":169170,"uid":72228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T05:04:42.000Z","msg":"樹大好心真係收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b332e7ac802b85c6c742a4d2d631f140d00c8513","tid":169170,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T05:10:15.000Z","msg":"小弟期望<br />\n<br />\n「過則勿憚改」，但希望佢地show到出黎真係有心改先<br />\n<br />\n反正底就一早起清哂，佢地再del相同資料都無用<br />\n<br />\n但我個人唔贊成再講樣，評頭品足/鬧樹大唔係大學之類，集中講件事，以免有位畀人入"},{"pid":"71b52cd9d91a14c69d7905aa542872488a73fb2d","tid":169170,"uid":88392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T05:19:46.000Z","msg":"推爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fac98ba8c291314b33a0c7f51b4882f881e0978","tid":169170,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T05:21:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/24/132142_a454369253145a9685f06238a5bfbe43.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F24%2F132142_a454369253145a9685f06238a5bfbe43.jpg&h=2943af3f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"37d4ea34e77bd409ea91e318b8de848963e55e87","tid":169170,"uid":88392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T05:22:51.000Z","msg":"呢班莊，為交代而道歉，有無諗過自己錯喺邊，道歉好似做show咁<br />\n枉為樹大生，仲話係系會，咁樣點對得住自己學校？好應該集體請辭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b157502045fb7b1d3ffa3be3a86d44f75d0fa2d","tid":169170,"uid":53413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T05:24:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43c0d40420391d17d71ae2a5c879f2a03c86d6a3","tid":169170,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T05:26:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢班莊，為交代而道歉，有無諗過自己錯喺邊，道歉好似做show咁<br />\n枉為樹大生，仲話係系會，咁樣點對得住自己學校？好應該集體請辭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n請辭都於事無補<br />\n<br />\n我希望跟進到佢地真係改就算"},{"pid":"0db8b21939b92ac86608c264ba43261afd824d4e","tid":169170,"uid":88392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T05:30:24.000Z","msg":"一早知自己去唔到，點解唔提早通知店家？<br />\n啲道歉聲明簡直係一篇垃圾，做大學生，基本嘅尊重都無？唔好諗住自己係莊就大撚晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人哋小店為咗你哋啲就職禮，廚師早返工幫你哋整<br />\n識唔識用腦諗吓人哋嘅心意？要刻意order材料，花時間心思製作<br />\n你哋聲都唔聲自己開party咁撚款，枉你哋開得落啦<br />\n人哋見你哋未到仲不停搵你哋，知唔知承諾兩隻字點寫？<br />\n咪撚出埋啲垃圾道歉文，用官腔打算耍走人就算<br />\n<br />\n最撚嬲係你哋為交代先至道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ced7bcaacd4f1053fb7c7da6a00255f2506fde98","tid":169170,"uid":88392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T05:31:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢班莊，為交代而道歉，有無諗過自己錯喺邊，道歉好似做show咁<br />\n枉為樹大生，仲話係系會，咁樣點對得住自己學校？好應該集體請辭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n請辭都於事無補<br />\n<br />\n我希望跟進到佢地真係改就算</blockquote><br 